Spotlight Card Analysis

Star Players

Cards expected to be highly effective. This includes cards that demonstrate their true value in critical late-game situations.

  • First Aid Kit
  • Full Moon Howl
  • Grimoire Study
  • Intelligent Sweeping Robot
  • Master of Collection
  • Neighbors from Hell
  • Open Universe
  • Starry Flight
  • True Full Moon
  • Water Blanket

Honor Students

Cards with exceptionally high tendency scores in both attack and defense or with silver(gold) medals, expected to perform consistently well in all situations.

  • Astrology Study
  • Ballistic Shield
  • Brain Overclock
  • Bright Starry Sky
  • Canned Food
  • Cooling Agent
  • Craft Potion
  • Dark Satellite
  • Fire of Ena
  • Hand Warmer
  • Mushroom Feast
  • Patchouli, Elemental Alchemist
  • Play With Water
  • Radioactive Elements
  • Red Star Explosion
  • Supernova
  • Supply Backpack

High-Potential Attackers

Cards with positive attack tendency and balanced defense.

  • Ageless Dream
  • Crimson Energy Release
  • Devil's Codex
  • Orrery's Sun
  • Parting Woes
  • Refine Potion
  • Spirit Assignment

Solid Defenders

Cards with positive defense tendency and balanced attack.

  • "Borrow" Materials
  • Directional Laser
  • Premeditation
  • Rocket Broom
  • Satellite Illusion

Counter Cards

Cards with low overall stats that have proven to be decisive (medal-winning) in specific, high-impact situations.

  • Emergency Defense
